create table "CON_ChargeItem"
(
"ChargeItemID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ZQChargeCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"ZQChargeName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"TChargeCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"TChargeName" NVARCHAR2(200),
"ChargeCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"OrderNum" INTEGER not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
constraint PK_CON_CHARGEITEM primary key ("ChargeItemID")
);
